#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:3
msgid "Starting up the partitioner"
msgstr "Yn cychwyn y rhaniadydd"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:11
msgid "Scanning disks..."
msgstr "Yn sganio disgiau..."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:15
msgid "Detecting file systems..."
msgstr "Yn canfod systemau ffeiliau..."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:31
msgid ""
"This partitioner doesn't have information about the default type of the "
"partition tables on your architecture.  Please send an e-mail message to "
"debian-boot@lists.debian.org with information."
msgstr ""
"Does gan y rhaniadydd hwn ddim gwybodaeth ynghylch math rhagosod y tablau "
"rhaniad ar eich pensaerniaeth. Os gwelwch yn dda, danfonwch ebost at debian-"
"boot@lists.debian.org gyda'r wybodaeth hon."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:31
msgid ""
"Please note that if the type of the partition table is unsupported by "
"libparted, then this partitioner will not work properly."
msgstr ""
"Sylwer os nad yw math y tabl rhaniad wedi ei gynnal gan libparted, yna ni "
"fydd y rhaniadydd yma yn gweithio'n iawn."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:42
msgid "Continue with partitioning?"
msgstr "Mynd ymlaen gyda'r rhaniadydd"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:42
msgid ""
"This partitioner is based on the library libparted which doesn't have "
"support for the partition tables used on your architecture.  It is strongly "
"recommended that you exit this partitioner."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r rhaniadydd hwn wedi ei seilio ar y llyfrgell libparted sydd heb "
"gynhaliaeth ar gyfer y tablau rhaniad a ddefnyddir ar eich pensaerniaeth. "
"Argymhellir yn gryf eich bod chi'n gadael y rhaniadydd hwn."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:42
msgid ""
"If you can, please help to add support for your partition table type to "
"libparted."
msgstr ""
"Os y gallwch, cynorthwywch gyda ychwanegu cynhaliaeth ar gyfer eich math "
"tabl rhaniad i libparted os gwelwch yn dda."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:52
msgid "No partitionable media"
msgstr "Dim cyfrwng rhaniadwy"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:52
msgid "No partitionable media was found."
msgstr "Ni chanfuwyd cyfrwn rhaniadwy."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:52
msgid "Please check that a hard disk is attached to this machine."
msgstr ""
"Os gwelwch yn dda, gwiriwch fod disgen galed wedi ei gysylltu i'r peiriant "
"hwn."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:60
msgid ""
"This is an overview of your currently configured partitions and mount "
"points. Select a partition to modify its settings (file system, mount point, "
"etc.), a free space to create partitions, or a device to initialise its "
"partition table."
msgstr ""
"Dyma grynodeb o'ch rhaniadau cyfredol a phwyntiau clymu. Dewiswch rhaniad er "
"mwyn newid ei osodiadau (system ffeiliau, pwynt clymu, a.y.y.b.), ofod rhydd "
"er mwyn creu rhaniadau, neu ddyfais er mwyn ymgychwyn ei dabl rhaniadau."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:65
msgid "Create new empty partition table on this device?"
msgstr "Creu tabl rhaniad newydd gwag ar y dyfais hwn?"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:65
msgid ""
"You have selected an entire device to partition. If you proceed with "
"creating a new partition table on the device, then all current partitions "
"will be removed."
msgstr ""
"Rydych wedi dewis dyfais cyfan i'w rhaniadu. Os ydych chi'n mynd ymlaen gyda "
"creu tabl rhaniad newydd ar y ddyfais hwn, yna caiff pob rhaniad cyfredol ei "
"ddinistrio."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:65
msgid "Note that you will be able to undo this operation later if you wish."
msgstr "Sylwer y cewch datwneud y weithred hon yn hwyrach os hoffech."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:75
msgid "Write a new empty partition table?"
msgstr "Ysgrifennu tabl rhaniad newydd gwag?"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:75
msgid ""
"Because of limitations in the current implementation of the Sun partition "
"tables in libparted, the newly created partition table has to be written to "
"the disk immediately."
msgstr ""
"Oherwydd cyfyngiadau yng nghôd tablau rhaniad Sun cyfredol libparted, rhaid "
"i'r tabl rhaniad newydd gael ei ysgrifennu at y ddsg ar unwaith."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:75
msgid ""
"You will NOT be able to undo this operation later and all existing data on "
"the disk will be irreversibly removed."
msgstr ""
"NI fyddwch yn gallu datwneud y weithred hon wedyn, a caiff yr holl ddata ar "
"y ddisg ei ddileu yn anadferadwy."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:75
msgid ""
"Confirm whether you actually want to create a new partition table and write "
"it to disk."
msgstr ""
"Cadarnhewch a ydych chi wir eisiau creu tabl rhaniad newydd a'i ysgrifennu "
"at ddisg."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:89
msgid "Continue with the installation?"
msgstr "Mynd ymlaen gyda'r sefydliad?"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:89
msgid ""
"No partition table changes and no creation of filesystems have been planned."
msgstr ""
"Nid oes newidiadau i'r tabl rhaniadau na chread systemau ffeiliau wedi eu "
"cynllunio."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:89
msgid ""
"If you plan on using already created filesystems, be aware that existing "
"files may prevent the successful installation of the base system."
msgstr ""
"Os ydych chi'n bwriadu defnyddio systemau ffeiliau sydd wedi eu creu "
"eisioes, sylwer gall ffeiliau sy'n bodoli eisioes rhwystro sefydliad "
"llwyddiannus y system sail."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:98
msgid "Write the changes to disks?"
msgstr "Ysgrifennu'r newidiadau at ddisgiau?"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:98
msgid ""
"If you continue, all changes in the partition tables will be written to the "
"disks."
msgstr ""
"Os ydych chi'n mynd ymlaen, caiff y newidiadau i'r tablau rhaniad eu "
"ysgrifennu at y disgiau."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:98
msgid ""
"WARNING: This will destroy all data on any partitions you have removed as "
"well as on the partitions that are going to be formatted."
msgstr ""
"RHYBUDD: Fe fydd hyn yn dinistio'r holl ddata ar y rhaniadau rydych chi wedi "
"dileu yn ogystal â'r rhaniadau a gaiff eu fformadu."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:98
msgid "${ITEMS}"
msgstr "${ITEMS}"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:109
msgid "The following partitions are going to be formatted:"
msgstr "Caiff y rhaniadau canlynol eu fformadu:"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. for example: "partition #6 of IDE0 master as ext3 journalling file system"
#: ../partman.templates:114
msgid "partition #${PARTITION} of ${DEVICE} as ${TYPE}"
msgstr "rhaniad #${PARTITION} o ${DEVICE} fel ${TYPE}"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:118
msgid "The partition tables of the following devices are changed:"
msgstr "Mae tablau rhaniad y dyfeisiau canlynol wedi newid:"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:123
msgid "Abort the partitioning and specify the next step?"
msgstr "Erthylu'r rhaniadu a phenodi'r cam nesaf?"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:123
msgid ""
"If you abort the partitioning, you will be given more control over the "
"installation process and you will be able to specify the next step."
msgstr ""
"Os ydych chi'n erthylu'r rhaniadu, cewch mwy o rheolaeth dros y broses "
"sefydlu a cewch benodi'r cam nesaf."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:123
msgid ""
"If you want to use the guided partitioning tool, do not abort the "
"partitioning, but choose \"Guided partitioning\" from inside the partitioner."
msgstr ""
"Os ydych am ddefnyddio'r offeryn rhaniadu tywysol, peidiwch ag erthylu'r "
"rhaniadu, ond dewiswch \"Rhaniadu tywysol\" o fewn y rhaniadydd."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:135
msgid "What to do with this device:"
msgstr "Beth i'w wneud gyda'r ddyfais yma:"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:140
msgid "How to use this free space:"
msgstr "Sut i ddefnyddio'r gofod rhydd hwn:"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:145
msgid "Partition settings:"
msgstr "Gosodiadau rhaniad:"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:145
msgid ""
"You are editing partition #${PARTITION} of ${DEVICE}. ${OTHERINFO} "
"${DESTROYED}"
msgstr "Rydych chi'n golygu rhaniad #${PARTITION} o ${DEVICE} . ${OTHERINFO} "
"${DESTROYED}"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:150
msgid "This partition is formatted with the ${FILESYSTEM}."
msgstr "Mae'r rhaniad hwn wedi ei fformadu gyda'r ${FILESYSTEM}."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:154
msgid "No existing file system was detected in this partition."
msgstr "Ni chafodd system ffeiliau sy'n bodoli ei ganfod yn y rhaniad hwn."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:158
msgid "All data in it WILL BE DESTROYED!"
msgstr "Caiff yr holl ddata ynfo EI DDINISTRIO!"

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:162
msgid "The partition starts from ${FROMCHS} and ends at ${TOCHS}."
msgstr "Mae'r rhaniad yn dechrau at ${FROMCHS} ac yn gorffen at ${TOCHS}."

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:166
msgid "The free space starts from ${FROMCHS} and ends at ${TOCHS}."
msgstr "Mae'r gofod rhydd yn dechrau at ${FROMCHS} ac yn gorffen at ${TOCHS}."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:170
msgid "Please wait..."
msgstr "Arhoswch os gwelwch yn dda..."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:174
msgid "Partitions formatting"
msgstr "Fformadu rhaniadau"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:178
msgid "Processing..."
msgstr "Yn prosesu..."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:190
msgid "Done setting up the partition"
msgstr "Gorffenwyd paratoi'r rhaniad"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:194
msgid "Finish partitioning and write changes to disk"
msgstr "Gorffen rhaniadau ac ysgrifennu'r newidiadau i'r ddisg"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:198
msgid "Undo changes to partitions"
msgstr "Datwneud newidiadau i rhaniadau"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman.templates:202
msgid "Show Cylinder/Head/Sector information"
msgstr "Dangos manylion Silindr/Pen/Sector"

